#summary A description of the file formats used in JSeat.
#labels fileformat

The following is a list of supported file types in JSeat
  * Version File (.ver)
  * Report Configuration File (.rep)
  * Class Metric data (.cme)
  * Method Metric data (.mme)
  * Dependency data (.dep)
  * JSeat Configuration File (.conf)
  * JSeat Project File (.jpf)
